https://account.netflix.com/TermsOfUse#arbitration  The relevant part is just below the arbitration paragraph.

"YOU AND NETFLIX AGREE THAT EACH MAY BRING CLAIMS AGAINST THE OTHER ONLY IN YOUR OR ITS INDIVIDUAL CAPACITY, AND NOT AS A PLAINTIFF OR CLASS MEMBER IN ANY PURPORTED CLASS OR REPRESENTATIVE PROCEEDING."

Without class action status it is more difficult to get recovery for small losses and removes an important consumer remedy.
